{"title":"地鸽","authors":["李富祺","丁午"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":8,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"地鸽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李富祺　诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁午　画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片洁白的云，张开翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它追求的是洁白的世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵飞翔的蒲公英，向着远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它追求的是洁白的憧憬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，地鸽却遗弃蓝天的爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只贪图金丝笼的安逸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它失去对拚搏的信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也失去对飞翔的忠诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它不敢向风暴扑击"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却召唤死一般的宁静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它不愿飞向拂晓前的黑暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却爱迷恋温柔的黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翅膀，不在追求中展开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那还有什么价值"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿飞翔，又想在天地浪漫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那简直是苍白的幻想"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}